title: [House Arcane, Cysaegir Lounge]
description: Dark, hardwood flooring is polished to a brilliant shine.  In one corner, a few tables and chairs are placed about a grey stone fireplace with a large iron log holder by its side.  On the other side of the room is a jade-inlaid ebonwood arch to the right and a jade velvet curtain that leads deeper into the annex.
